flowRoot.flowPara: A hakerspace based in Birmingham, fizzPOP is a collection of people with a wide range of skills and interests, bound by a common urge to tinker, to make new things and to learn.

Be it electronics, art, science, lockpicking, mechanics, knitting, computing, music, open source software or something yet to be dreamt up. fizzPOP aims to be a place to foster collaboration and to share skills and interests with one another.
We invite you to come along for a chat and a look around.
